    <div class="col-md-5"> <strong><h3>About Students Helper</h3></strong>
       <strong><p>Can Help to:</p></strong>
        <ol>
            <li>Popularization of research work;</li>
            <li>Appropriation of work already done in a specific area in order to avoid doing the same things;</li>
            <li>Collect contributions and suggestions from specialists in order to better orient research work;</li>
            <li>Share the exam tests, the courses (texts, images, videos etc ....) and scientific opinions;</li>
            <li>Learn the concepts of courses from different media (texts, images, videos etc ...);</li>
            <li>Solving specific problems of pupils and students;</li>
            <li>Limit the use of home tutors for students;</li>
            <li>Establish contacts between learners (pupils, students) on the one hand and between students and teachers on the other hand;</li>
            <li>Facilitate the collection of exam tests and any other didactic support by pupils and learners;</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
