    <div class="col-md-5"> <strong><h3>How to use Students Helper</h3></strong>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Sign up</strong> to complete the registration form. Do not forget to mention his status (Pupil, Student or Teacher);</li>
            <li>For registration, Email and Password can't be blank;</li>
            <li><strong>Login</strong> with the correct information;</li>
            <li><strong>New Post </strong>for a new publication with a title, content and possibility of associating any type of file (PDF, Word, Excel, Photo, video etc ...);</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2"> 
