    <div class="col-md-5">
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Post List</strong> allows you to access all published posts;</li>
            <li><strong>Show</strong> allows you to see the details of a post;</li>
            <li>On the post details page, you can choose as favorites, comment on the post and have access to other users' comments;</li>
            <li><strong>User List</strong> allows you to see the list of all users in order to facilitate exchanges;</li>
            <li><strong>Admin Screen</strong> is only accessible to administrator users and allows you to manage all models;</li>
            <li>The <strong>Back</strong> button allows you to go back or return to the list of posts;</li>
